<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV95">
<l>yātāṉu mōrāk kaiyiṟpukkaṅ kāppuṇṭu māppaviḻntu</l>
<l>mūtāvi yiṟṟaṭu māṟu muyirmuṉṉa mēyataṉāl</l>
<l>yātāṉum paṟṟinīṅ kumvira tattainal vīṭuceyyum</l>
<l>mātā viṉaippitu vaittiru mālai vaṇaṅkuvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Entering a body of any kind, absorbing bondage there and bondage opening</l>
<l>the life of old souls used to be unsteady, formerly. Therefore,</l>
<l>I shall bow to the mother, the father, to Tirumāl</l>
<l>who makes conduct that leaves off seizing anything into good liberation.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
